Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.55,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}coming for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.55,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all I ever wanted to do was do right things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.18,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never wanted to be the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.10,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I swear
