Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:13.02,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never wanted to grab a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.11,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.82,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tearless, fearless,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.91,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}burning, burning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.91,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you tell me what have I missed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.75,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}still wandering in the deep mist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.59,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all, slip and fall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.55,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will never look away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:45.77,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all, lose it all, lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.35,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if I lose it all outside the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.73,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:58.32,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't want anything I'm just here to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:02:59.99,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Beware
